data.description: Great opportunity! Check out this HUGE 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home and minutes from Amarillo in Panhandle TX. This home has SO MUCH to offer. It has two living areas, one of which can be used as a media room or even that 5th BEDROOM! The isolated 4th bedroom will make a perfect guest bedroom as it has an isolated entrance as well as its own mini splits for extra cooling in this summer sun! The GOURMET KITCHEN has ample room to host many people. With a big SUNROOM, formal dining space, and a breakfast bar, this home is definitely an entertainer's dream! Per seller- Newer Vanity, floor, paint in master bath. Newer carpet in master, sunroom, and 4th bedroom.  Newer paint in the living room and 2 bedrooms. Newer windows in the sunroom. Schedule your private showing today
